headline: Cencora Announces Date and Time for Second Quarter Fiscal 2025 Earnings Release
summary: CONSHOHOCKEN, Pa., March 28, 2025--Cencora, Inc. (NYSE: COR) today announced that it plans to release its results for the Second Quarter of Fiscal 2025 on Wednesday, May 7, 2025, prior to the opening of trading on the New York Stock Exchange. The Company will host a conference call to discuss the results at 8:30 a.m. ET on May 7, 2025.
